      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Grasp the Great Sword",
        "Client": "Master Utsushi",
        "Description": "Alright, Ace, lesson time!\r\nThe \u003CCOL RED\u003EBishaten\u003C/COL\u003E may move and\r\nattack in its own unique way,\r\nbut when it hits big, it hits BIG!\r\nSee for yourself what I mean,\r\nand you\u0027ll definitely find new\r\nways to swing a great sword!",
        "Target": "Hunt 2 Bishaten",
        "Fail": "Reward hits 0, or time expires"
      },
      {
        "Language": "FRE",
        "Name": "Le\u00E7on grande \u00E9p\u00E9e",
        "Client": "Utsushi le ma\u00EEtre",
        "Description": "Bon, je t\u0027explique ! Le \u003CCOL RED\u003EBishaten\u003C/COL\u003E\r\na sa propre mani\u00E8re de bouger et\r\nd\u0027attaquer, mais quand il frappe,\r\ncrois-moi \u00E7a fait mal ! Si tu\r\nen rencontres un, tu comprendras,\r\net la grande \u00E9p\u00E9e te servira !",
        "Target": "Chasser deux Bishaten",
        "Fail": "Prime \u00E0 0 ou temps expir\u00E9"
      },
      {
        "Language": "ITA",
        "Name": "Brandisci lo spadone",
        "Client": "Maestro Utsushi",
        "Description": "OK, \u00E8 ora di imparare: il\r\n\u003CCOL RED\u003EBishaten\u003C/COL\u003E si muove e attacca\r\nin modo unico ma, quando\r\ncolpisce, lo fa con GRANDE\r\nforza. Scoprilo da te e\r\nimparerai nuovi modi per\r\nbrandire lo spadone!",
        "Target": "Caccia 2 Bishaten",
        "Fail": "Premio a zero o tempo scaduto"
      },
      {
        "Language": "GER",
        "Name": "Gebrauch des Gro\u00DFschwerts",
        "Client": "Meister Utsushi",
        "Description": "Okay, Ass, aufgepasst! Der\r\n\u003CCOL RED\u003EBishaten\u003C/COL\u003E bewegt sich vielleicht\r\nauf seine eigene Weise, aber\r\nwenn er trifft, trifft er HART!\r\nSieh selbst, dann wirst du neue\r\nWege finden, das Gro\u00DFschwert\r\nzu schwingen!",
        "Target": "Erjage zwei Bishaten.",
        "Fail": "Belohnung auf 0 oder Zeit\r\nl\u00E4uft ab."
      },
      {
        "Language": "SPA",
        "Name": "Blande la gran espada",
        "Client": "Maestro Utsushi",
        "Description": "Puede que los \u003CCOL RED\u003EBishaten\u003C/COL\u003E no sean\r\nrivales f\u00E1ciles, pero un golpe\r\nfuerte es un golpe fuerte.\r\nVe a comprobar a qu\u00E9 me\r\nrefiero y aprender\u00E1s nuevas\r\nformas de esgrimir la gran\r\nespada.",
        "Target": "Caza 2 Bishaten",
        "Fail": "La recompensa cae a 0\r\no se acaba el tiempo"
